-- Bank of East Asia Said to Hire Citigroup, JPMorgan for 10-Year Bond Issue
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-23T03:03:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-23/bank-of-east-asia-said-to-hire-citigroup-jpmorgan-for-10-year-bond-issue.html

          
          
                  June 23 (Bloomberg) -- Bank of East Asia Ltd.  hired
Citigroup Inc. and JPMorgan Chase & Co. to help it sell
subordinated 10-year bonds in dollars, according to a person
with direct knowledge of the matter.  
 The banks are meeting potential investors in Hong Kong
today before traveling to Singapore tomorrow, the person said.  
 -- Henry Sanderson . Editor:  Will McSheehy   
